EventItemActionText: A motion was made that this Land Use Call-Up be Approved, by Council approved by consent Roll Call.
EventItemTitle:
By The Chair of the Land Use Committee (Council Member Salamanca):
Pursuant to Rule 11.20(b) of the Council Rules and Section 197-d(b)(3) of the New York City Charter, the Council hereby resolves that the actions of the City Planning Commission on Uniform Land Use Review Procedure Application Nos. C 180486 PCK, C 180488 ZSK, and C 180490 ZSK (Marcus Garvey Village) shall be subject to Council review.  These applications are related to Application Nos. C 180485 HAK, C 180487 ZRK, and C 180489 ZMK.
EventItemMatterName: Zoning, Marcus Garvey Village, Brooklyn (C 180486 PCK, C 180488 ZSK, 180490 ZSK, C 180485 HAK, C 180487 ZRK, and C 180489 ZMK)

EventItemActionText: A motion was made that this Land Use Call-Up be Approved, by Council approved by consent Roll Call.
EventItemTitle:
By Council Member Kallos:
Pursuant to Rule 11.20(b) of the Council and §20-225 of the New York City Administrative Code, the Council resolves that the action of the Department of Consumer Affairs approving an enclosed sidewalk café located at 300 East 86th Street, Borough of Manhattan, Council District 5, Community District 8, Application No. 20195184 TCM shall be subject to review by the Council.
EventItemMatterName: Zoning, Sidewalk café, 300 East 86th Street, Manhattan (20195184 TCM)
